The photo included in the first tweet in the article was used widely over
social media tagged with #Gaza and #Palestine, but its origin is unknown. If
you know the original source, kindly provide it in the comments section below.

The citation of these campaigns does not signify the author's endorsement. The
campaigns included in this post are examples of those mentioned on social
media. There are many other funding opportunities available if you would like
to support the people of Gaza through registered nonprofits.

